# Notice for ffts-grep

This work is based on an idea originally proposed by **Leo** (@leocooout).

## Original Inspiration

The concept of using SQLite FTS5 for file indexing in Claude Code was first described by Leo in their public discussion:
- https://x.com/leocooout/status/2009337600742707335

## Attribution

We thank **[@leocooout](https://x.com/leocooout)** for sharing this approach publicly, which inspired the development of this implementation.

